title: 100 Button Mystery BOAT!.. One Button SINKS You!
author: Dangie Bros
description:
DONT press the wrong mystery button on this 100 button mystery boat! Only 1 button lets you escape BUT 1 button will sink your boat! This is a brand new hilarious twist to the 100 mystery button box trend that we started. Now we are making it even better! This is the Worlds funniest edition to the mystery button trend every YouTuber on the planet has done. I hope this boat is unbreakable.. can we survive the Dangie waters or will we end up underwater.. Winner gets to press the golden mystery button which has a hidden secret punishment for the loser. It's very satisfying seeing Chris and Jeff get absolutely covered in some of the nastiest punishments YouTube has seen!  Being trapped on this boat is not where you want to be!
